---
name: get_recent_triage_events
description: >
  Returns recent triage alerts logged in OmniAnalytix. Each alert has a
  severity (critical, warning, info), a type (e.g. Budget, Inventory,
  Compliance), a title and message, the platform it relates to, and whether
  it has been resolved. Accepts an optional 'limit' (default 20, max 50) to
  control how many events are returned. Use this when the user asks about
  recent alerts, active issues, triage events, or platform warnings.
---
Pass `unresolved_only: true` when the user wants the active issue list.
